name: Pokimane [Reupload]
description:
Award-winning Twitch streamer and YouTuber Pokimane, now available for Stable Diffusion through textual inversion!

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. The training set included a few images of her with curly hair as well, so adding 'curly hair' to your prompt should easily change her hairstyle. Any limits you might encounter with the embedding can be countered by using inpainting or lowering the weight in your prompts.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
